hotspot.title: Home Information
hotspot.description: This home is located moments away from Lake Wailes Lake, Kawanis Park, and Historic Downtown Lake Wales. It features original wood floors, 9 foot ceilings, and a private garden. Call Joan Jarvis at Prime Plus Real Estate for more information at (863) 676-7040. See more photos of the property HERE

hotspot.title: Patio Information
hotspot.description: The patio is a screened enclosure with tile floors, ceiling fan, and measures at 7 feet 10 inches by 17 feet 11 inches.

hotspot.title: Living Room
hotspot.description: The living space is a sprawling 28 feet 6 inches by 14 feet 2 inches. Complete with hardwood floors, a beautiful fireplace, and view of your own private garden.

hotspot.title: Dining Room
hotspot.description: The dining room has access to the private garden, and measures 12 feet 5 inches by 16 feet. Plenty of room for holidays and family gatherings.

hotspot.title: The Kitchen
hotspot.description: The kitchen features floor to ceiling cabinets, tile counter tops and propane gas stove. It is 12 feet 4 inches by 8 feet 10 inches, plenty of room to cook amazing meals for the family!

hotspot.title: Back Patio
hotspot.description: This secluded patio has access from the kitchen, and a bedroom. It has a path to the rear carport, and measures 15 feet 5 inches by 7 feet 7 inches.

hotspot.title: Office Space
hotspot.description: This room could be a bedroom, or office space. It has access to the backyard and measures 12 feet by 10 feet. The closet measures 2 feet 9 inches by 4 feet 10 inches, and has lots of space for storage!

hotspot.title: Bathroom 1
hotspot.description: The first of 2 bathrooms in this home, hase tile and a standing shower. Measures 4 feet 10 inches by 7 feet 9 inches.

hotspot.title: Bedroom 1
hotspot.description: This bedroom has private access to the rear patio, and has 2 large closets and built in storage. Measurements for the room are 10 feet by 14 feet 6 inches. Closets are 2 feet 2 inches by 4 feet 6 inches each. Plenty of storage for two.

hotspot.title: Bedroom 2
hotspot.description: This room is very large, measuring 11 feet 5 inches by 16 feet 3 inches. It also has a large closet 2 feet by 5 feet 8 inches.

hotspot.title: Laundry Room
hotspot.description: Laundry room complete with hook ups and measuring 8 feet 4 inches by 8 feet 3 inches.

hotspot.title: Bathroom 2
hotspot.description: This beautiful bathroom has fresh tile, and fixtures and has plenty of space 6 feet 10 inches by 8 feet 5 inches.

hotspot.title: Bedroom/Playroom
hotspot.description: This is yet another large bedroom that comes with a large closet. Measurements on the room are 13 feet by 12 feet. The closet is 3 feet by 6 feet 6 inches. All of the kids toys will fit in there!
